defaultWe are pleased that t
defaulthe g
defaultovernment has 
defaultsaid that they will consult on their plans for restricting judicial review 
defaultas 
defaultit is vital that they look again at this issue to ensure that this basic 
defaultprotection and mechanism for holding 
defaultpublic authorities to account is not
default eroded.
default&#xa0;
defaultNow that the government has published further details on their plans it is clear that 
defaultthe earlie
defaultr
default stages of judicial review work
default 
defaultonly 
defaultremain
default within the scope of legal aid 
defaultby way of a discretionary payment schem
defaulte.
