defaultcases whose outcome can often be uncertain.  This could effectively remove access to judicial review for otherwise important and arguable cases.
default&#xa0;
defaultThere is 
defaultalso 
defaulta risk this will change the behaviour of public authorities because they will anticipate relucta
defaultnce to take judicial review beyond a threat to application stage. This could be seriously 
defaultdetrimental to those in need of services such as housing, social care and education
