defaultRestricting the scope of legal aid for prison law
defaultWhilst
default&#xa0;
defaultwe agree that it would be reasonable for more trivial issues to be dealt with by the Prison Ombudsman Service rather than through legal aid,
default&#xa0;
defaultwe are
default&#xa0;
defaultconcerned that if 
